      "test": "stm32f407vet6_iwdg",
      "reason": "EXCLUDED from suite: after IWDG test completes, board enters continuous IWDG-reset loop (IWDGRSTF set on every boot, firmware re-enters Phase2, never kicks IWDG, resets again). This breaks SWD and prevents re-flashing without BOOT0 recovery. Test plan and firmware preserved but must not be run in automated suites."
